    "body": "The loop is emulating a condvar here (specifically `cvBestBlock`), but I don't see a good way to deal with `fDisconnect` in a cond-wait that isn't quite a bit more involved than fixing this little data race. If init ran in a boost thread it'd be interruptible, but nothing in `AppInit2` expects to be exitable via interruption exceptions... utACK 46b0c3b; I'll open a separate bug relating to `fDisconnect`\n",
